WEBVTT

00:03.592 --> 00:08.592
Subtitles by explosiveskull

00:10.000 --> 00:16.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

00:34.121 --> 00:35.755
What is everybody
makin' such a big thing for?

00:35.757 --> 00:37.857
You'd think the
tomato was a queen.

00:37.859 --> 00:40.225
As far as you're
concerned, she is.

00:40.227 --> 00:42.361
Trouble, I can give it to you.

00:51.973 --> 00:53.839
It was hard enough to
get a good job in this town,

00:53.841 --> 00:56.177
and I don't want to lose it.

01:02.717 --> 01:03.949
You know
all about the fishes,

01:03.951 --> 01:06.351
'cause you're at
home in the slime.

01:06.353 --> 01:07.587
You've put your finger
on all the bodies

01:07.589 --> 01:10.958
that have been buried,
but you won't tell.

01:13.328 --> 01:15.028
Guess I'm
not supposed to ask you

01:15.030 --> 01:16.129
if you've been following me.

01:16.131 --> 01:16.932
Why?
No.

01:18.500 --> 01:21.904
But I suppose
it was all right.

01:25.974 --> 01:27.473
Wouldn't you say
that gives you control

01:27.475 --> 01:29.375
of these bookies?

01:29.377 --> 01:30.911
No, I wouldn't.

01:30.913 --> 01:32.613
That's what they like to say
about me, czar of the bookies,

01:32.615 --> 01:34.280
that's nonsense, it isn't true.

01:34.282 --> 01:37.219
I lend money just
like a bank does.

01:41.289 --> 01:45.258
You can forget this
guy, we can get Ackerman.

01:45.260 --> 01:47.994
We will,
we've got Conelly.

01:47.996 --> 01:49.562
Don't talk, Jerry.

01:49.564 --> 01:53.235
Oh Jerry.

02:38.815 --> 02:41.348
Call.

02:41.350 --> 02:43.753
You sure you wanna do that?

02:48.558 --> 02:49.393
All in.

02:53.630 --> 02:56.701
Alright.

02:58.468 --> 03:00.805
This just got interesting.

03:05.776 --> 03:06.877
Full house.

03:07.745 --> 03:08.979
Aces over twos.

03:15.085 --> 03:15.920
Oh my god.

03:17.755 --> 03:19.254
Sorry Danny.

03:19.256 --> 03:21.123
That sucks.

03:21.125 --> 03:22.192
Wait, what?

03:24.461 --> 03:25.761
What are the odds?

03:25.763 --> 03:27.662
What are the odds
you'd deal quads?

03:27.664 --> 03:30.432
What, you think I don't
know this game is rigged?

03:30.434 --> 03:31.900
What's your cut?

03:31.902 --> 03:33.168
Huh?
No one forced you to play.

03:33.170 --> 03:34.436
Yeah, great job
dealer, great job.

03:34.438 --> 03:35.805
That's on you.

03:35.807 --> 03:37.406
No one forced you to
play tonight Danny.

03:37.408 --> 03:38.607
That's on you.

03:38.609 --> 03:39.542
Come on man, take it easy.

03:39.544 --> 03:40.777
Grab your coat.

03:40.779 --> 03:42.111
Yeah I can walk
my own self out.

03:42.113 --> 03:44.413
Hey what's your problem?

03:44.415 --> 03:45.782
Hope you feel good
about yourselves.

03:45.784 --> 03:47.616
That's my niece's tuition.

03:47.618 --> 03:49.185
Just walk it off Danny.

03:49.187 --> 03:51.187
Walk it
off, walk this off.

03:51.189 --> 03:52.023
Yeah.

04:16.447 --> 04:19.684
Get up Bella, you
have deadlines to meet.

04:26.993 --> 04:29.493
We're live on the scene
with Daniel Collins.

04:29.495 --> 04:32.398
Sir, are you having
a good morning?

04:35.367 --> 04:36.202
Well?

04:38.704 --> 04:39.705
Well what?

04:40.739 --> 04:42.408
You don't have it?

04:43.876 --> 04:47.144
Bell I'm trying to enjoy my
breakfast so can't this wait?

04:47.146 --> 04:50.080
I need to get this in before
the deadline, Uncle Danny.

04:50.082 --> 04:51.984
This is more important.

04:57.857 --> 05:00.858
I'm sorry Bella,
I don't have it.

05:00.860 --> 05:02.192
What?

05:02.194 --> 05:03.293
None of it?

05:03.295 --> 05:05.631
No, I promise I'll get it.

05:07.499 --> 05:08.899
Are you serious?

05:08.901 --> 05:10.500
I can't believe you.

05:10.502 --> 05:12.437
And take a shower
for God's sake.

05:12.439 --> 05:15.042
You reek of liquor and all ins.

05:34.494 --> 05:36.461
What's up Bella?

05:36.463 --> 05:37.963
Where you going pretty lady?

05:37.965 --> 05:40.598
Juanito, give me
my hat and move.

05:40.600 --> 05:42.067
What was that?

05:42.069 --> 05:45.070
You should be lucky
I'm even trying to talk to you.

05:45.072 --> 05:46.204
I don't like you.

05:46.206 --> 05:47.738
Stick to your
business with my uncle

05:47.740 --> 05:49.040
and leave me alone.

05:50.477 --> 05:51.311
Alright.

05:55.382 --> 05:57.482
Tell your uncle he
can't run forever.

05:57.484 --> 05:58.583
I want my money.

05:58.585 --> 05:59.753
Get in line.

06:01.455 --> 06:03.791
See you later Bella.

06:10.899 --> 06:12.698
Damn girl, don't
you know how to knock?

06:12.700 --> 06:13.966
What's if I was naked?

06:13.968 --> 06:15.634
There's nothing to see anyway.

06:15.636 --> 06:17.803
Yeah, says you.

06:17.805 --> 06:18.938
Getting ready?

06:18.940 --> 06:20.139
Yeah.

06:20.141 --> 06:24.043
I don't wanna leave
anything to last minute.

06:24.045 --> 06:24.879
Yeah.

06:29.117 --> 06:30.716
What's the matter?

06:30.718 --> 06:33.052
You're really leaving, huh?

06:33.054 --> 06:35.354
Yeah, just Boston.

06:35.356 --> 06:38.190
I'll be back by Thanksgiving,
maybe even Christmas.

06:38.192 --> 06:41.529
Besides, you'll be
busy with school too.

06:43.697 --> 06:45.466
You are going, right?

06:46.534 --> 06:48.201
Doesn't look like it.

06:48.203 --> 06:50.737
My uncle doesn't have the money.

06:50.739 --> 06:51.972
What?

06:51.974 --> 06:54.241
I thought he was
saving it for you.

06:54.243 --> 06:57.777
I shoulda never
trusted him with it.

06:57.779 --> 06:58.948
Why did you?

07:00.849 --> 07:03.350
Well, I only had
half the money.

07:03.352 --> 07:05.018
And he said he knew a way

07:05.020 --> 07:06.519
that he could double
it in one night.

07:06.521 --> 07:07.689
So I said yes.

07:08.857 --> 07:10.123
He was so sure he
could score with it

07:10.125 --> 07:11.693
and I believed him.

07:12.827 --> 07:14.962
Bella I'm so sorry.

07:14.964 --> 07:16.196
Is there anything I can do?

07:16.198 --> 07:18.133
Don't worry about it.

07:19.534 --> 07:21.468
No, we both said we
were gonna leave together.

07:21.470 --> 07:24.037
I don't wanna see you
stuck here either.

07:24.039 --> 07:27.376
If it's meant to
be then it'll happen.

07:29.244 --> 07:31.178
You're my best friend.

07:31.180 --> 07:33.448
I just want you to be happy.

07:35.217 --> 07:36.684
You're gonna get outta here.

07:36.686 --> 07:41.624
You're gonna see the world
and you're gonna be a writer.

07:42.358 --> 07:43.726
I'm going to miss you.

07:45.996 --> 07:48.064
I'm gonna miss you too.

07:54.237 --> 07:55.336
Hey Deanna.

07:55.338 --> 07:56.270
How are you today?

07:56.272 --> 07:57.107
Hey.

07:58.208 --> 07:59.507
I'm good.

07:59.509 --> 08:01.344
I got your favorite.

08:04.647 --> 08:06.114
I don't have time
for a song today

08:06.116 --> 08:07.915
but you're going to
sing for me, right?

08:07.917 --> 08:09.585
I definitely will.

08:10.453 --> 08:13.554
You just so good to me Bella.

08:13.556 --> 08:14.855
Well I better get inside

08:14.857 --> 08:18.126
before Mr. Cliff comes
out looking for me.

08:18.128 --> 08:19.129
Okay baby.

08:21.931 --> 08:23.064
Hey everybody.

08:23.066 --> 08:24.401
Bella.

08:26.203 --> 08:29.238
Like I said, you know they
gonna win the MPP this year.

08:30.407 --> 08:31.806
Hey man let me tell you,

08:31.808 --> 08:34.143
me and this dude go back
further than the Bronx airline.

08:43.919 --> 08:45.487
Bella, Bella
you're killing me.

08:45.489 --> 08:47.622
Why do you keep giving that
woman reasons to loiter

08:47.624 --> 08:49.058
in front of my shop?

08:49.060 --> 08:49.958
What?

08:49.960 --> 08:51.893
Wow, you see everything.

08:51.895 --> 08:53.962
And she was out there before
I started working here.

08:53.964 --> 08:55.430
Yeah and you know how
many time I've run her off.

08:55.432 --> 08:59.403
Come on, gimme a break
with her already, please.

09:03.740 --> 09:05.240
Yo yo yo Danny.

09:05.242 --> 09:07.276
Hey listen, hey
man when you gonna

09:07.278 --> 09:09.678
pay me back that 50
bucks you owe me?

09:09.680 --> 09:11.346
I don't owe you 50 bucks.

09:11.348 --> 09:12.915
Oh I figured since
you owed everybody else

09:12.917 --> 09:14.184
you probably owed me too.

09:15.087 --> 09:15.920
I got him.

09:18.290 --> 09:19.955
Ya'll seen him do it.

09:19.957 --> 09:21.859
How's everybody know?

09:22.894 --> 09:24.360
Bella say something?

09:24.362 --> 09:26.196
It gets around pretty quick
when you play high stakes

09:26.198 --> 09:28.300
like you were last night.

09:30.202 --> 09:33.371
Cliff, can I talk
to you in private?

09:37.375 --> 09:38.474
Sure.

09:38.476 --> 09:39.377
Come on in.

09:48.320 --> 09:49.552
Hey Bruno.

09:49.554 --> 09:51.354
Hey Bella.

09:51.356 --> 09:52.855
You still read the paper?

09:52.857 --> 09:54.857
You know you can get news
on your phone nowadays.

09:54.859 --> 09:57.793
Call me a
dinosaur, but I love the way

09:57.795 --> 10:00.231
a newspaper feels
on my fingertips.

10:00.233 --> 10:03.066
Plus, less radiation
going through my veins.

10:03.068 --> 10:07.173
Well if you say so.

10:12.511 --> 10:14.178
Take care of her
this time, huh?

10:14.180 --> 10:14.980
Yeah.

10:20.253 --> 10:21.452
I'd like to talk to Cliff.

10:21.454 --> 10:22.519
Can I go in?

10:22.521 --> 10:23.922
Sure, go ahead.

10:30.429 --> 10:32.028
Hi Cliff.

10:32.030 --> 10:32.896
Can I come in?

10:32.898 --> 10:34.531
Sure, yeah.

10:34.533 --> 10:35.368
Thanks.

10:36.335 --> 10:37.503
Have a seat.

10:40.606 --> 10:43.440
So, what can I help you with?

10:43.442 --> 10:45.642
Why was my uncle here?

10:45.644 --> 10:49.481
Bella I, I hear that
you're having money problems.

10:49.483 --> 10:52.250
Uncle Danny said I
had money problems?

10:52.252 --> 10:53.851
He's the one with
money problems.

10:53.853 --> 10:56.354
He was supposed to be
saving my money for school.

10:56.356 --> 10:57.855
Ask him where that's at.

10:57.857 --> 11:02.294
Oh right, you can't because
he doesn't have any of it.

11:02.296 --> 11:03.863
Bella, stay calm.

11:06.833 --> 11:08.833
Did he tell you
where the money went?

11:08.835 --> 11:10.468
Or does he owe you too?

11:10.470 --> 11:11.736
No.

11:11.738 --> 11:14.408
He came here for something else.

11:16.210 --> 11:17.411
Something else.

11:20.747 --> 11:24.984
Now look, I think I can
help you with your problem.

11:26.220 --> 11:29.254
I know someone who works
over at the university.

11:29.256 --> 11:30.890
She owes me a favor.

11:37.798 --> 11:39.300
Will you call her?

11:40.435 --> 11:42.503
Yes Cliff, I sure will.

11:45.606 --> 11:46.541
Call her!

11:55.950 --> 11:56.784
Bella.

11:58.118 --> 11:58.953
Hey.

12:01.088 --> 12:02.521
Bell!

12:02.523 --> 12:03.791
Dinner's ready.

12:39.395 --> 12:40.627
Yes I'll send you

12:40.629 --> 12:43.297
a list of potential
students by tomorrow.

12:43.299 --> 12:45.932
Mrs. Mackie, your
9:00 o'clock is here.

12:45.934 --> 12:49.002
Will do, thanks.

12:49.004 --> 12:50.437
Bella, right?

12:50.439 --> 12:51.405
Yes ma'am.

12:51.407 --> 12:52.574
Have a seat.

12:55.043 --> 12:57.877
So Clifford says you wanna
try and get into school?

12:57.879 --> 12:59.646
Yes ma'am.

12:59.648 --> 13:01.214
You're gonna have to say a
little more than yes ma'am.

13:01.216 --> 13:02.482
I have to know how to help you.

13:02.484 --> 13:03.950
You want some water?

13:03.952 --> 13:05.285
Yes ma'am.

13:05.287 --> 13:07.253
Yes, I would like some water.

13:07.255 --> 13:09.489
Shari a couple waters please.

13:09.491 --> 13:12.092
Look, if Danny's not in the
house, we leave a message.

13:12.094 --> 13:12.927
Not home.

13:12.929 --> 13:13.763
Done.

13:18.701 --> 13:20.935
So tell
me about yourself

13:20.937 --> 13:22.603
and your desired major.

13:22.605 --> 13:24.138
Journalism, actually.

14:30.708 --> 14:33.675
- Anything?
- I got nothing.

14:33.677 --> 14:35.345
Nothing here boss.

14:37.448 --> 14:39.481
You will be eligible
for all those scholarships

14:39.483 --> 14:41.450
that we talked about.

14:41.452 --> 14:44.019
Just gather the documents
requested, get 'em back to me

14:44.021 --> 14:45.220
and I'll help you
fill out the rest.

14:45.222 --> 14:47.323
Thank you so much Mrs. Mackie.

14:47.325 --> 14:48.591
My pleasure.

14:48.593 --> 14:50.693
You should be able to
enroll by next semester.

14:50.695 --> 14:53.062
I can't thank you enough.

14:53.064 --> 14:53.898
Thank you.

15:33.371 --> 15:35.004
Bella can we talk?

15:35.006 --> 15:36.239
I'm getting dressed.

15:36.241 --> 15:39.512
Besides, there's
nothing to talk about.

15:40.513 --> 15:41.679
Yesterday, I...

15:41.681 --> 15:42.880
Save it.

15:42.882 --> 15:44.381
I'm handling it.

15:44.383 --> 15:45.315
I don't need you anymore.

15:45.317 --> 15:46.886
Now leave me alone.

16:38.572 --> 16:39.538
Bella!

16:47.514 --> 16:49.848
Where are you going?

16:49.850 --> 16:51.816
What are you wearing?

16:51.818 --> 16:52.884
I know.

16:52.886 --> 16:55.286
I feel really awkward.

16:55.288 --> 16:57.057
So you don't like it?

16:58.424 --> 17:01.325
It's just I've never
seen you in a dress before.

17:01.327 --> 17:03.595
And without your hat.

17:03.597 --> 17:05.598
Well, that says a lot.

17:07.500 --> 17:09.200
What do you want me to say?

17:09.202 --> 17:10.801
That maybe I look
as pretty as that girl

17:10.804 --> 17:13.204
that you were dancing with.

17:13.207 --> 17:14.040
Better.

17:15.309 --> 17:18.277
Where is this coming from?

17:18.279 --> 17:19.280
Nevermind.

17:21.648 --> 17:24.950
When did you start caring
about the girls you see me with?

17:24.952 --> 17:25.885
Nevermind.

17:25.887 --> 17:27.319
Forget I said anything.

17:27.320 --> 17:29.054
Go enjoy your party.

17:29.056 --> 17:30.389
Bella!

17:30.391 --> 17:31.225
Bella!

17:41.102 --> 17:43.235
Uncle Danny I'm home.

17:44.706 --> 17:45.738
Uncle Danny?

17:45.740 --> 17:47.272
Uncle Danny!

17:47.274 --> 17:48.307
Oh my god are you okay?

17:48.309 --> 17:49.476
What happened?

17:50.377 --> 17:51.278
Hey Bell.

17:53.380 --> 17:55.049
No, no, no no no no.

17:55.917 --> 17:57.418
Shh, shh, no cops.

17:58.285 --> 17:59.119
You are hurt.

17:59.121 --> 18:00.153
You need an ambulance.

18:00.155 --> 18:02.257
No, no I'm not.

18:03.358 --> 18:04.490
I can't.

18:04.492 --> 18:06.361
I gotta get help.
No, no.

18:16.772 --> 18:17.704
Hello.

18:17.706 --> 18:18.538
Cliff.

18:18.540 --> 18:19.372
Yeah.

18:19.374 --> 18:21.174
Uncle Danny's hurt.

18:21.176 --> 18:22.876
He's on the ground.

18:22.878 --> 18:25.545
He's at our house,
somebody attacked him.

18:25.547 --> 18:26.479
What?

18:26.481 --> 18:27.681
He's on the ground.

18:27.683 --> 18:28.682
Who did this?

18:28.684 --> 18:30.617
I don't know who did it.

18:30.619 --> 18:32.252
Alright, alright, just relax.

18:32.254 --> 18:33.486
I'll be right over.

18:33.488 --> 18:35.055
I'll be right over.

18:35.057 --> 18:37.257
Okay, come quick.

18:37.259 --> 18:38.524
I'll be here.

18:38.526 --> 18:40.493
Bruno, we have a situation.

18:40.495 --> 18:42.863
I need you to pick me up,
drop me off at Bella's

18:42.865 --> 18:44.665
and then head over to Juanito's.

18:44.667 --> 18:48.569
And make sure that they know
that Danny's debt is canceled.

18:48.571 --> 18:50.171
Yeah.

18:50.173 --> 18:53.274
Yeah, this generation needs
to learn some respect.

18:53.276 --> 18:54.110
Son of a.

19:17.333 --> 19:18.334
- Hey.
- Hey.

19:27.310 --> 19:28.644
So, how is he?

19:30.413 --> 19:32.847
They really beat him badly.

19:32.849 --> 19:35.352
Mr. Cliff's upstairs with him.

19:37.321 --> 19:39.822
Bella I'm so sorry.

19:39.824 --> 19:41.890
Is there anything I can do?

19:41.892 --> 19:43.291
No.

19:43.293 --> 19:44.693
I just feel really bad

19:44.695 --> 19:48.731
by the way I've been
treating Uncle Danny lately.

19:48.733 --> 19:51.867
I said a lotta
things I didn't mean.

19:51.869 --> 19:53.568
I'm sure he understands.

19:53.570 --> 19:55.570
He loves you too much.

19:55.572 --> 19:57.672
Besides you can't feel bad

19:57.674 --> 20:00.809
for what he gets
himself involved in.

20:00.811 --> 20:01.645
I guess.

20:03.547 --> 20:05.382
So, how was the party?

20:07.184 --> 20:10.819
It would've been
better if you stayed.

20:10.821 --> 20:12.289
Bell, are we okay?

20:13.590 --> 20:15.357
Yeah, no worries.

20:15.359 --> 20:17.392
I was just having a moment.

20:17.394 --> 20:18.195
Bell?

20:19.129 --> 20:20.097
Are we good?

20:21.265 --> 20:22.066
Yes.

20:33.511 --> 20:35.344
Do you want something to drink?

20:35.346 --> 20:36.181
No.

20:39.918 --> 20:42.487
Why are you weirding out on me?

20:44.823 --> 20:46.057
I don't know.

20:47.158 --> 20:50.393
I just feel like things
are falling apart.

20:50.395 --> 20:53.062
I guess I don't want
you to leave me.

20:53.064 --> 20:54.931
I'm not gonna leave you.

20:54.933 --> 20:58.436
I'm a phone call and
a 10 hour drive away.

20:59.570 --> 21:02.171
Things are getting
dangerous here.

21:02.173 --> 21:03.508
I just wanna go.

21:05.076 --> 21:08.111
They could've killed
my uncle tonight.

21:08.113 --> 21:09.881
It's gonna be okay.

21:11.050 --> 21:13.583
Now listen, it's okay.

21:20.827 --> 21:22.226
I need you to go pick up
that package on 18th Street.

21:24.130 --> 21:25.264
Go get that.

21:55.727 --> 21:58.028
Where do you
think you're going?

22:02.369 --> 22:04.069
How much does Danny owe you?

22:05.605 --> 22:07.205
How much?

22:07.207 --> 22:08.539
Nothing.

22:08.541 --> 22:12.143
Please,
make me come back.

22:27.427 --> 22:29.260
Mrs. Mackie.

22:29.262 --> 22:31.062
Hey Bella, I'm
just checking in.

22:31.064 --> 22:32.330
I haven't heard from
you in a couple of days.

22:32.332 --> 22:33.631
Everything alright?

22:33.633 --> 22:35.566
I'm sorry, I've been
taking care of my uncle.

22:35.568 --> 22:37.102
He was in an accident.

22:37.104 --> 22:39.337
Oh wow, I'm
sorry to hear that.

22:39.339 --> 22:40.273
Is he okay?

22:41.208 --> 22:43.008
Yes ma'am, he's doing better.

22:43.010 --> 22:44.775
Okay well you still
wanna come to school

22:44.777 --> 22:46.177
this next semester, right?

22:46.179 --> 22:48.514
Yes, I filled out
most of the paperwork.

22:48.516 --> 22:50.182
Have I missed the deadline?

22:50.184 --> 22:53.185
Oh no you have a week
to get those forms to me.

22:53.187 --> 22:54.987
